.
PowerShell Script.
Is to be synchronised via acadon_PSM mechanism.

Script evaluates the actual login. Asks the user which user to evaluate.
Fetches Data (Givenname SurName Title Location ..) and askes User to confirm every field.
Searches for Language Directorys in the Scriptdirectory and let the User Choose which languages should be used.
Copys every File from selected Languages to the _local_Outlook path [Sync to web is to be done by outlook] ,
at that replacing @@placeholder@@ with value. 
For a rtf file the umlaut äöüßÄÖÜ will by replaced.

Embedded Logos and Icons as base64 strings

Status: 
Languages: CH DE DK EN FR NL ; 

User Information is fetched via LDAP from AD ; 

CMD to start the local synchronised acadon_PSM version added ; ZIP container with this CMD for Email / Website distribution added
